2 SECTION 43, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
3 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 1. (a) The bureau (as defined in IC 4-33-2-3.7)
4 shall provide information to a certificate holder or vendor concerning
