1 is delinquent in child support, the certificate holder or vendor:
2 (1) may deduct and retain an administrative fee in the amount of
3 the lesser of:
4 (A) three percent (3%) of the amount of delinquent child
5 support withheld under subdivision (2)(A); or
6 (B) one hundred dollars ($100); and
7 (2) shall:
8 (A) withhold the amount of delinquent child support owed
9 from winnings;
10 (B) transmit to the bureau:
